column5: Just thought I'd try to post a picture & see how it turns out, Ian's 3rd day on the lake, he flipped & pitched & I threw spinnerbaits most of the day, lots of bass, we were happy with our results even though I blew a bigger fish 10 minutes into the day 7th 13.39 lbs   15.54lbs won it Richard
I know that lake.Hold great bass.  Congrats on yer 7th finish.
